    "text": "I hereby give consent to Casa de la Familia's clinicians to conduct psychotherapy with the child named in this packet. I confirm that I am the parent/guardian to the child named in this packet. I consent that all material discussed during the psychotherapy sessions is confidential and can be released only with the permission of the minor in therapy. I understand special sensitivity may be required in releasing information about certain topics such as drugs and sex. I will accept Casa de la Familia's judgment in regard to releasing or sharing information obtained during the course of psychotherapy with the minor that may endanger or jeopardize the client's wellbeing."
